<p style="margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-family: verdana, geneva; font-size: 12pt;">We have prepared for you 3 error scenarios that may appear in your Zscaler application. Click on the related case to see the detailed solution.</span></p>
