<tr style="height: 686px;">
<td style="width: 33.3333%; height: 686px;"><details>
<summary><span style="font-family: verdana, geneva; font-size: 12pt; cursor: pointer;"><strong><span style="color: #c00000;">Case 1 -</span><span style="color: #c00000;"> Basic Zscaler Troubleshooting Steps</span></strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><span style="color: #0000ff;">(click to expand/minimize)</span></span></summary>
<p style="margin: 0in; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin: 0in; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="color: black; font-family: verdana, geneva; font-size: 12pt;"><strong>Solution:</strong> </span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="color: black; font-family: verdana, geneva; font-size: 12pt;">Go to More menu in Zscaler application and click on following options in sequence:</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: verdana, geneva; color: black;">1. Click on&nbsp;<strong>Update Policy</strong>&nbsp;to renew Zscaler&rsquo;s policies</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: verdana, geneva; color: black;">2. Click on&nbsp;<strong>Update App</strong> to update application</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: verdana, geneva; color: black;">3. Click on&nbsp;<strong>Repair App</strong></span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: verdana, geneva; color: black;">4. Click on&nbsp;<strong>Restart Service</strong></span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: verdana, geneva; color: black;">5. Go to&nbsp;<strong>Private Access</strong>&nbsp;(lock icon) and connect to Zscaler again</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: verdana, geneva; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="color: black;"><img src="/sys_attachment.do?sys_id=2c51d62b87e28dd0489cfc89cebb35d9" width="529" height="389" /></span> </span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin: 0in; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin: 0in; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</p>
</details></td>
<td style="width: 33.3333%; height: 686px;"><details>
<summary><span style="font-family: verdana, geneva; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="cursor: pointer;"><strong><span style="color: #c00000;">Case 2 - <span style="cursor: pointer;"> Authentication error </span></span></strong><span style="color: #c00000;"><span style="cursor: pointer;"><span style="color: #0000ff;">(click to expand/minimize)</span></span></span></span></span></summary>
<p><span style="font-family: verdana, geneva; font-size: 12pt;"><strong>Solution:</strong></span></p>
<ol style="list-style-position: inside;">
<li style="font-family: verdana, geneva; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-family: verdana, geneva; font-size: 12pt;">Open the Zscaler application</span></li>
<li style="font-family: verdana, geneva; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-family: verdana, geneva; font-size: 12pt;">Pay attention to the tab &ldquo;Private access&rdquo;, click on &ldquo;Authenticate&rdquo;</span></li>
</ol>
<p><span style="font-family: verdana, geneva; font-size: 12pt;"><img src="/sys_attachment.do?sys_id=5d77562387668dd0489cfc89cebb3500" width="470" height="289" /></span></p>
<ol style="list-style-position: inside;" start="3">
<li style="font-family: verdana, geneva; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-family: verdana, geneva; font-size: 12pt;">Follow the OKTA log in by entering your <strong>email</strong> and <strong>password</strong> from your laptop</span></li>
<li style="font-family: verdana, geneva; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-family: verdana, geneva; font-size: 12pt;">After the process is finished, the Zscaler will be closed automatically</span></li>
<li style="font-family: verdana, geneva; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-family: verdana, geneva; font-size: 12pt;">Please, open the apps and internet pages &ndash; they should work now</span></li>
</ol>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
</details></td>
<td style="width: 33.3333%; height: 686px;"><details>
<summary><span style="font-family: verdana, geneva; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="cursor: pointer;"><strong><span style="color: #c00000;">Case 3 - "Your session expired due to idle timeout" </span></strong><span style="color: #c00000;"><span style="cursor: pointer;"><span style="color: #0000ff;">(click to expand/minimize)</span></span></span></span></span></summary>
<p><span style="font-family: verdana, geneva; font-size: 12pt;"><strong>Solution:</strong></span></p>
<ol style="list-style-position: inside;">
<li style="font-family: verdana, geneva; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-family: verdana, geneva; font-size: 12pt;">First step is clicking the BACK arrow</span></li>
</ol>
<p><span style="font-family: verdana, geneva; font-size: 12pt;"><img src="/sys_attachment.do?sys_id=e8d716a387668dd0489cfc89cebb354a" width="207" height="145" /></span></p>
<ol style="list-style-position: inside;" start="2">
<li style="font-family: verdana, geneva; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-family: verdana, geneva; font-size: 12pt;">Once you receive the login screen again, click on LOGIN button</span></li>
</ol>
<p><span style="font-family: verdana, geneva; font-size: 12pt;"><img src="/sys_attachment.do?sys_id=a8d7d2a387668dd0489cfc89cebb35cf" width="447" height="307" /></span></p>
<ol style="list-style-position: inside;" start="3">
<li style="font-family: verdana, geneva; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-family: verdana, geneva; font-size: 12pt;">Follow the OKTA log in process by entering your email and password from your laptop</span></li>
<li style="font-family: verdana, geneva; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-family: verdana, geneva; font-size: 12pt;">After the process is finished, the Zscaler will be closed automatically</span></li>
</ol>
</details></td>
